---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Pipe Replacement"
  description={`Expert pipe replacement services in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC from the licensed pros at Nesbitt's Plumbing. Call ${site.phone} today.`}
  heroTitle="Does Your Home Need New Pipes?"
  heroSubtitle="Call us for pipe replacement services in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-24.jpg"
  listHeading="When should you replace your pipes?"
  listItems={[
    'Blocked or slowed water flow',
    'Corrosion or rust',
    'Leaks from pipes or joints',
    'Cracks or broken areas',
    'Deteriorated pipe lining',
  ]}
  listNote="We make replacing your pipes easy. Contact our office today to schedule an appointment."
  ctaHeading="Ready to Replace Your Aging Pipes?"
>
  <p>
    After years of use and exposure to water, the pipes in your home will need to be replaced.
    When you need expert pipe replacement services, you can count on the pros at Nesbitt's
    Plumbing to get the job done right. Our team of professionals will skillfully and efficiently
    replace pipes in your home in Hendersonville or Asheville, NC.
  </p>
  <p>
    Call <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    now to get more information about replacing your plumbing system.
  </p>
  <p>
    There are several warning signs that your pipes are no longer functioning as they should —
    if you notice any of the symptoms listed here, it's time to consider a pipe replacement.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
